data.description: Ask about the Assumable 3.25% VA loan! This exquisite 2-story residence is the epitome of luxurious living, complete with a private pool + spa! Nestled in highly sought-after Santa Rita Ranch, the stunning interior boasts hardwood flooring, high ceilings, & an abundance of natural light that floods every corner of the home. Work from home in style with a dedicated home office featuring elegant French doors, providing privacy & tranquility. Host lavish dinner parties in the formal dining room, or unwind in the spacious living room with its soaring ceiling & magnificent stone fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for cozy evenings. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with a center island, breakfast bar, pristine white cabinetry, granite countertops, & top-of-the-line stainless-steel appliances. On the main floor, discover your private owner's suite, a true sanctuary featuring a generously sized walk-in closet & a spa-like bath with a dual vanity, makeup area, soaking tub, & separate walk-in shower. An additional bedroom & full bath on the main floor make it ideal for accommodating guests or multigenerational living. Venture upstairs to find 2 more bedrooms.  The game room & media room provide additional opportunities for entertainment & leisure. Step outside into your own private backyard oasis, where a covered patio & pergola provide shade & comfort. Immerse yourself in the refreshing in-ground pool & spa, creating memories to last a lifetime. Whether you're hosting summer barbecues or simply enjoying a quiet evening outdoors, this backyard is the perfect haven for relaxation & recreation. But the perks don't end there! Santa Rita Ranch offers a plethora of amazing community amenities, including a clubhouse, pools, splash pads, water slides, parks, pavilions, playgrounds, sports courts, trails, & much more. Experience the best of an active & vibrant community right at your doorstep. Schedule a showing today!
